description: Treat .tf files as TinyFugue scripts rather than Terraform
globs: "**/*.tf"
alwaysApply: false
---

# TinyFugue Scripts

- **File type:** Files with the `.tf` extension are TinyFugue script files, not Terraform.
- **Preserve script semantics:** Do not apply Terraform formatting, linting, naming, or module conventions to these files.
- **Reference docs:** TinyFugue command and topic references are available at:
  - http://flaprider.dyndns.org/~hair/tf/commands/index.html
  - http://flaprider.dyndns.org/~hair/tf/topics/index.html
